            <div class="col-md-12"><h2>Order procedure Dutch</h2>
                <p>The ordering process is made easy for a customer to order quickly and with little effort. There may be some stuff in the shopping cart by logging in and selecting a product that the customer would like to have on the product page. If the customer has any product that he / she wants to order in the shopping cart, he can go to the shopping cart page by selecting at the top of the website for shopping cart. Here the customer can see previous orders and what's in the shopping cart. To order all products from the shopping cart, the customer orders to order. This leads the customer to the order overview page. Here the customer can review his order and make sure everything is correct.
                                        If the order is below 50 euros, the customer pays 2 euros shipping. These fall away at an additional cost of 50 euros. Below is the payment method chosen by the customer when registering. This can be changed via the 'My Account' page. When everything is right, the customer presses the order at the bottom and then the order is paid and the customer receives an email confirmation.
                </p>
